Brasil Foods Offers to Buy Nilza’s Milk Unit, Estado Reports

-- B y   J e s s i c a   B r i c e
-- 
2011-05-25T12:10:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-25/brasil-foods-offers-to-buy-nilza-s-milk-unit-estado-reports.html
BRF - Brasil Foods SA (BRFS3) , the world’s
largest poultry exporter, offered to buy a dairy unit for about
60 million reais ($37 million), O Estado de S. Paulo reported.  Brasil Foods  began talks to buy the unit, which produces
long-life milk in  Sao Paulo  state, from Industria de Alimentos
Nilza, the newspaper reported.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jessica Brice in Sao Paulo at 
 jbrice1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dale Crofts at 
 dcrofts@bloomberg.net . 